Trust ME!! I have a love hate relationship with wallpaper! I LOVE the instant fun and pattern it brings to a room! I see so many good ones, I just want them all!! I’m a SWITCHER / SWAPPER type of gal, so the glue on type kinda freaks me out. I want the freedom to peel it off at a moments notice! I know it sounds like I am a  crazy lady. 🤷‍♀️ Which when it comes to decorating and design I am! Just ask my family! I’m not trying to sell wallpaper… I bought all the papers willingly and happily! 🤣 What I am selling is… BE CREATIVE in your home! It doesn’t have to cost a lot to make changes and move things around. I’m your home cheerleader! I mess up all the time or things don’t work! It’s never perfect and that’s ok. Join me in taking a risk on the place you call HOME. It’s FUN and I’m cheering you on!! #homecheerleader #wallpaper #home #design #decorate #peelandstickwallpaper #oregon #trusttheprocess #reels

Pedal Home Interiors excited to host an exclusive Organizing Workshop featuring Kim Snodgrass, owner of Rustic Home Organizing. Join us for an inspiring session as Kim shares her expert tips and tricks for creating a home that's truly cherished!

At Pedal Home Interiors, we believe that a home should be a special place that reflects your unique personality and style. We understand the importance of organization, as well as the perfect balance of functionality and beauty. It's the key to transforming any living space into a haven you'll adore.

Our delightful workshop will take place on the charming Pedal Home outdoor patio, offering a lovely and relaxed atmosphere. As you soak in the knowledge, we'll treat you to delectable nibbles and refreshing drinks. And that's not all – there will be exciting opportunities for private shopping and chances to win fabulous prizes from the Pedal Home Interiors shop.

Seats for this event are limited, so make sure to reserve yours promptly. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to elevate your home to new heights of style and organization! We can't wait to welcome you to our inspiring workshop! To save your seat and purchase your tickets, please visit the link in bio.
